# .dockerignore
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.git/
**/.gitignore
**/.dockerignore
**/Dockerfile
**/docker-compose*.yml
**/README*.md
**/.env
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/Properties/launchSettings.json

# Node modules (if any)
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log

# Build outputs
**/publish/
**/out/

# Test files
**/test*
**/*test*
**/*Test*

# Documentation
**/docs/
**/*.md